abstract: Bombings in commercial areas of Baghdad kill at least 15 people and wound dozens of others.
lead_paragraph: A string of bombings ripped mainly through commercial areas in the capital, Baghdad, on Sunday, killing at least 15 people and wounding dozens, officials said.
